      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORNING DAYLIGHT (6) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 5.5 lengths (22.18) at this track. Hard to go past. MY HARLEY (5) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on April 14 over 388m at this track behind Silent Minute beaten one length (22.54). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Can measure up. MAGIC TECHNIQUE (1) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at The Gardens over 400m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to feature again. STORMY LANE (2) is not to be discarded.",
